  "text": "It should be noticed that this theory underwent a large number of iterations before the WwW principle was finally elucidated properly and shown to give the right results. The number and complexity of the test calculations needed to debug, develop and validate the theory presented in this paper necessitated the development of a bespoke \"UTP Calculator\" [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
